description:
BENEFITS of THIS COURSE and WHAT YOU WILL LEARN

  1. You will learn the 12 Career Archetypes - the patterns and tendencies we all bring to career.
  2. You will be able to explore many alternative possibilities for fulfilling career paths that align with the ancient wisdom of your astrological birth chart.
  3. You will understand what energies you bring to any career choice.
  4. You will learn the difference between ‘what you do’ daily and ‘who you become’ in the public eye.
  5. Leave this course with a basic understanding of astrology and how to apply it practically in your life towards a fulfilling and successful career.
  6. Discover how to effectively manage your energy and efficiently use your gifts daily
  7. Learn what energies in your daily environment may stress or exhaust you as well as cause illness.
  8. You will save time on the path to living your vocational calling, while gaining confidence stepping in to your highest service on the planet.
  9. Famous Examples for every career path
  10. Multi-Format learning: Audio, Video, Mindmaps, JPGs, and Keynote presentation
  11. Guarantee - If you're not fully satisfied with this course in the first 30 days, you will receive a full refund.
title: Discover Your Optimum Career Path with Basic Astrology
